topics.script:
if (getFlag("chef", "escapebroached")){
    play("\"If you haven’t already noticed, it’s not like anywhere else you’ve ever been. It’s a sort of island, but it’s a strange sort of water what lies between here and home – The sort only the master knows how to navigate.\"")
}else{
    play("\"If you haven’t already noticed, it’s not like anywhere else you’ve ever been. It’s a sort of island, but it’s a strange sort of water what lies between here and home – The sort only the master knows how to navigate. \" \n \n \*\*New topic available: \"Escape?\"\*\*")
