    play("\"Yes...hmmm...the passcode. Funny thing. I can\'t remember it. Whenever Master wanted me to remember, he had me make the Eggs Benedict. The smell always jogged it back out of me. But then he\'d take the recipe back, and I\'d forget all over again.\"")
